<p>Video formats designed with mobile in mind include our <a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-29996475">60 second</a> explainers and the 15-second <a href="http://instagram.com/bbcnews/">BBC Shorts</a> appearing on Instagram.</p>
 
